---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/icon.svg" />
        <link rel="alternate icon" type="image/png" sizes="48x48" href="/icon48.png" />
        <link rel="alternate icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/icon16.png" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <title>Privacy Policy | Sharp Tabs</title>
        <meta
            name="description"
            content="Privacy Policy for Sharp Tabs Chrome Extension, including details on data handling and AI features."
        />

    </head>
    <body class="min-h-screen bg-[#03060f] transition-colors duration-300">
        <Navbar />
        <main class="mx-auto mt-24 max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 text-white/80">
            <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: June 6th, 2025</p>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Your Privacy Matters</h2>
                <p>
                    Sharp Tabs is designed with your privacy in mind. We do <b>not</b> collect, log, or store any personal
                    data or browsing history. Your information remains on your device and is never sent to the developer.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">1. What We Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    Sharp Tabs does <b>not</b> collect any personal or sensitive data. The only data we store is related
                    to your Sharp Tabs account (if you register): your email address, registration date, email verification
                    status, and subscription details. We might also store which features are enabled or disabled in the future.
                    <b>No browsing history, tab details, or personal content is ever collected.</b>
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">2. AI Features and Data Usage</h2>
                <p>
                    AI features are available for premium users or anyone using their own Gemini API key. Only the names of your
                    tabs and the beginning of their URLs are sent to Gemini's API to organize your tabs or name a group. <b
                        >Nothing else is sent to Gemini. Nothing is logged or stored. Nothing is ever sent to the
                        developer.</b
                    > You can always toggle off all AI featuresâ€”they are completely optional.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">3. No Tracking or Analytics</h2>
                <p>
                    Sharp Tabs does <b>not</b> use any installed tracking scripts or third-party cookies. Your browsing activity
                    is never monitored or analyzed.
                    <br />
                    We only optionally Anonymously track the non-sensitive applied settings (once per day max when you close
                    the settings page), this is to get stats about which settings are most used, and help guide development.
                    You can easily toggle this off at any time in the general settings section at the top of the settings
                    page.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">4. Data Security</h2>
                <p>
                    We take your privacy seriously. All data related to your account is securely stored and never shared
                    with third parties. You can delete your account at any time, and all associated data will be
                    removed.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    If this policy changes, we will update this page. By continuing to use Sharp Tabs, you agree to the
                    latest version of the policy. We will add a notice on the app's settings when this is done.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">6. Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a
                        href="mailto:support@sharptabs.com"
                        class="text-blue-400 underline">support@sharptabs.com</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </section>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
